General.Name: Artrya Ltd
General.Description: Artrya Limited operates as a medical technology company that uses artificial intelligence (AI) to identify patients at risk of coronary artery disease. It offers Salix, a cloud-based software that uses its AI to automate the detection of coronary artery disease from coronary computed tomography angiography. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in West Perth, Australia.
